description:
The 6’5” Australian cheek clapper fell in love on Netflix’s hit reality TV series ‘Too Hot To Handle,’ only to end up with a broken heart and a one way ticket to Los Angeles. In this episode, we discover Logan and Harry are Eskimo bros, talk about how and when relationships go wrong, the key to lasting more than 60 seconds in bed, and more...
